SPELL NAME  : Cloud of Shining Sparks
SPELL SYNTAX: Cloud <target>
SPELL COST  : 20+2*Guild Level
DESCRIPTION : The Cleric may summon the essence of good spirits from another
	      plane to aid the Cleric by distracting his foe and even by
	      causing minor pain to his foe. The distraction will end when
	      all the sparks have been destroyed.
